{{Infobox Artwork
| image_file=Virtù e due scene 02.jpg
| image_size=300px
| title=Cardinal and Theological Virtues
| artist=Raphael
| year=1511
| type=fresco
| dimensions={{convert|6.6|m|ft|abbr=on}} wide
| city=Vatican City
| museum=[[Vatican Museums]]
